313
00:11:47,876 --> 00:11:49,627
Obrigado,
Holly J Sinclair.

314
00:11:49,711 --> 00:11:50,628
(TODOS APLAUDEM)

315
00:11:50,712 --> 00:11:52,255
Parabéns.

316
00:11:52,338 --> 00:11:53,798
(A PLATÉIA VIBRA)

317
00:11:53,882 --> 00:11:55,425
