entre nós esta noite!

444
00:16:12,432 --> 00:16:13,808
♪ Ba-ba-ba-ba-balancem ♪

445
00:16:13,892 --> 00:16:15,768
♪ Nós sabemos ♪

446
00:16:15,852 --> 00:16:17,312
♪ Nós te conhecemos... ♪

447
00:16:18,313 --> 00:16:20,064
